# NTNT Language Website
# Official website for ntnt-lang.org
# Run: ntnt intent check server.tnt

## Overview
A clean, modern website introducing the NTNT programming language.
Built with NTNT's file-based routing, external templates, and middleware.

## Design
- Colors: #137EA2 (teal), #F1993F (orange), #2C2A74 (indigo), #192F52 (navy), #FCDD83 (yellow), #20DDE3 (cyan)
- Hero: Full 100vw edge-to-edge, warm premium gradient (indigo → violet → orange glow)
- Header: Dark glass effect with backdrop blur, floating over hero
- Clean, modern aesthetic with responsive design

---

## Glossary

| Term | Means |
|------|-------|
| a visitor goes to $path | GET $path |
| page loads successfully | status 200, returns HTML |
| returns HTML | header "Content-Type" contains "text/html" |
| has site branding | body contains "ntnt-logo", body contains "NTNT" |
| has navigation | body contains "Learn", body contains "Blog" |
| has proper layout | has site branding, has navigation, body contains "footer" |
| they see {text} | body contains {text} |
| they don't see {text} | body not contains {text} |
| page not found | status 404 |
| blog post exists | status 200, returns HTML |
| blog post missing | body contains "Post Not Found" |

