Feature: Code Quality
  id: feature.code_quality
  description: "Server code passes linting and validation checks"

  Scenario: All code is valid
    description: "All .tnt files pass linting and validation"
    When checking code quality
    → code is valid
    → no syntax errors
    → no lint warnings

